### Calcular team strengths para una competición
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/team-strengths/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "season": "2024",
  "competition_id": 1,
  "matchday": 20,
  "league_factor": 0.90
}

###

### Calcular team strengths — Champions League (factor 1.0)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/team-strengths/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "season": "2024",
  "competition_id": 2,
  "matchday": 6,
  "league_factor": 1.0
}

###

### Registrar logro: Real Madrid campeón de Champions
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/achievements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "competition_id": 2,
  "team_id": 5,
  "season": "2024",
  "phase": "winner",
  "rules_version_id": 1
}

###

### Registrar logro: equipo llega a semifinal
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/achievements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "competition_id": 2,
  "team_id": 10,
  "season": "2024",
  "phase": "semi_final",
  "rules_version_id": 1
}

###

### Error case: fase inválida → 400
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/achievements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "competition_id": 2,
  "team_id": 5,
  "season": "2024",
  "phase": "fase_inventada",
  "rules_version_id": 1
}

###

### Error case: rules_version_id inexistente → 404
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/achievements
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "competition_id": 2,
  "team_id": 5,
  "season": "2024",
  "phase": "winner",
  "rules_version_id": 9999
}

###

### Calcular bonuses por logros competitivos
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/scoring/achievements/calculate-bonuses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "season": "2024",
  "competition_id": 2,
  "rules_version_id": 1
}

###

### Ranking versionado con sfa_total (incluye bonuses)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ranking?season=2024&rules_version_id=1&use_total=true&limit=10

###

### Ranking legacy (backward-compat, sin bonuses)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ranking?season=2024&limit=10

###
